{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：14:47 2026-04-27 HKT<br/>發佈時間：14:47 2026-04-27 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：14:47 2026-04-27 HKT</p><img alt=\"呂健威今早大舉練兵\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl_square/3893c7bea3356d3b6e2c40165c343b96/2026-04/dddd.jpg\"/><p>呂健威今早在烽火台坐陣，多匹周三有程馬均有出操。其中何澤堯親為「勇敢孖寶」主課在大圈快跳，其他參戰馬「雙星報喜」、「巴閉王」、「君至酷」、「合夥飛馳」均有亮相，磨刀霍霍，各匹參戰馬備戰如火如荼，倉主期望周三各駒能盡力跑出好成績。</p><p>按圖睇有關相片：</p><img alt=\"K126 「雙星報喜」\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl/0ca37e107360eb9bc841287b42bbf18c/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-27_at_11_03_08_2_.jpeg\"/><img alt=\"LOO8 「君至酷」\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl/25b52fdcac9569752b7bbde3170bb824/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-27_at_11_03_08_3_.jpeg\"/><img alt=\" 「合夥飛馳」K342。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl/9b63529691df08dac27e553c376940d6/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-27_at_11_03_08.jpeg\"/><img alt=\"何澤堯「勇敢巨星」G268\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl/9baefe6ed69f9476ec1103f9a28ef772/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-27_at_11_03_09_1_.jpeg\"/><img alt=\"「巴閉王」(K479)\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl/f6d9a8f66149059817369bedad0e12e9/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-27_at_11_03_09.jpeg\"/><p>陳嘉甜</p><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-27T07:01:11.640610+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":210,"images":6,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}